snippet.title: Cresselia vs Darkrai | Pokémon Sleep
snippet.description:
Darkrai approaches with a nightmare, but Cresselia is ready to transform everyone's Drowsy Power into strength to fight back!

Stay tuned for more announcements for the Cresselia vs Darkrai event coming March 2025! #PokemonSleep #PokemonDay
